title: Exclusive picture from Kumari 21F
text: Kumari 21F, which stars Raj Tarun and Hebah Patel in lead roles, is currently under production and the makers are releasing on the sets pictures on a regular basis. Here's one more picture from the movie which will see both Raj Tarun and Hebah making their debut in Tollywood. D irected by Palnati Surya Pratap, the music of the film will be composed by Devi Sri Prasad .
